{DIALOGUE}: We must get him to my father.
{DIALOGUE}: Strider quickly lifts Frodo...placing him on the horse.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ARWEN (CONT'D)
{DIALOGUE}: I have been looking for you for two days.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PIPPIN
