{DIALOGUE}: I'm the faster rider.
{DIALOGUE}: Strider clamps his hand over Arwen's.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: STRIDER
{META_DATA}: (elvish:subtitles)
{DIALOGUE}: Andelu I ven.
{DIALOGUE}: The road is too dangerous.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: ARWEN
{META_DATA}: (Elvish: subtitles)
{DIALOGUE}: Frodo Fir.
{DIALOGUE}: Ae anthradon I hir, tur gwaith nin beriatha hon. If I can cross the river, the power of my people can protect him.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: PIPPIN
{DIALOGUE}: What are they saying?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: CLOSE ON: Arwen reaches for Strider's hand...looking deep into his eyes.
