{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 62.
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: EXT. PINE FOREST -- DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The white horse charges through a Pine Forest.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Suddenly 2 Galloping Ringwraiths emerge from the trees behind!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 2 more Ringwraiths slide in from different directions to join the chase.
