{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: BOOM the sound of the drums rings out again!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Gandalf turns to the others.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: GANDALF
{DIALOGUE}: To the bridge of Khazad-dum!
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. DWAROWDELF CHAMBER, MORIA -- DAY
