{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Frodo looks with horror at the overwhelming Goblin army that's rushing toward them!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: SUDDENLY!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A deafening roar fills the air!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: A fiery light dances down the hallway... the pillars casting eerie shadows.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Goblins freeze.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They back Fearfully away from the approaching beast...melting into the darkness.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: BOROMIR
{DIALOGUE}: What is this new devilry?
