{CHARACTER_NAME}: GANDALF
{META_DATA}: (quietly)
{DIALOGUE}: A Balrog.
{DIALOGUE}: a demon of the ancient world!
{DIALOGUE}: This foe is beyond any of you!
{META_DATA}: (urgent yell)
{DIALOGUE}: Run!
{DIALOGUE}: Quickly!
{META_DATA}: CUT TO:
{SCENE_BOUNDARY}: INT. STAIRWAY OF KHASAD-DUM, MORIA -- DAY
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The BALROG, a massive creature rises from a chasm, a great 40 foot man-beast, with a mane of flames!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: In one hand is a blade...like a stabbing tongue of fire; in the other, a WHIP of many thongs.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Aragorn leads the fellowship to the top of a dizzying stairway...Gandalf follows, leaning heavily on his staff.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Close on: Aragorn looks at Gandalf, concerned.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: GANDALF
{DIALOGUE}: Lead them on, Aragorn.
{DIALOGUE}: The bridge is near.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Aragorn hesitates...Gandalf looks at him.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: GANDALF (CONT'D)
{DIALOGUE}: Do as I say; swords are no more use here.
