{DIALOGUE}: Over the bridge!
{DIALOGUE}: Fly!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: They race towards the slender bridge of stone...without kerb or rail...at the far end of the hall.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The Fellowship recklessly hurry over the dizzying bridge.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: but Gandalf... the last.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: pauses in the middle of the span...he faces the Balrog...staff in one hand...Sword in the other!
