{DIALOGUE}: The dark fire will not avail you, flame of Udun.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Frodo watches as the Balrog puts one foot on the bridge and draws up to Full Height, wings spreading from wall-to-wall.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Gandalf is a tiny figure, balanced precariously on the narrow bridge.
