{DIALOGUE}: Go back to the shadow!
{DIALOGUE}: The BALROG slashes at Gandalf with its Sword of
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: flame...Gandalf blocks with his sword...a ringing clash and the Balrog's sword shatters into molten fragments!
