{META_DATA}: (CONTINUED)
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: 97.
{META_DATA}: CONTINUED:
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: He thumps the bridge with his staff...a blinding sheet of white flame springs up... the staff shatters...the bridge breaks... right at Balrog's feet.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: The stone bridge drops away into the gulf...from under the Balrog.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: For a moment, the great Beast remains poised in the air...then it plunges down: in slow motion Relief floods Frodo's face.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Gandalf remains trembling on the lip of the broken bridge.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Slow motion: As the Balrog falls, he lashes out with his whip of fire... Slow motion: The thongs of the whip lash and curl around Gandalf's knees, dragging him over the brink!
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Gandalf just manages to hand on by his fingertips
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FRODO
