{CHARACTER_NAME}: SAM
{DIALOGUE}: We may yet, Mr. Frodo.
{DIALOGUE}: We may.
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FRODO
{DIALOGUE}: Sam?
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: Frodo looks at Sam with great affection.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: despite the grim outlook, Sam is undeterred...
{CHARACTER_NAME}: FRODO (CONT'D)
{DIALOGUE}: I'm glad you're with me.
{SCENE_DESCRIPTION}: WIDE ON: THE TWO HOBBITS SETTING OFF TOWARD MORDOR.
{META_DATA}: THE END
